div.head:
49. Telegram From the Department of State to the Embassy in IranSource: National Archives, Nixon Presidential
                        Materials, NSC Files, Box 603, Country
                        Files—Middle East, Iran, Vol. V, May–December 1973. Secret; Niact;
                        Immediate; Nodis. Drafted by Dickman; cleared in draft by Donaldson and by Morton (NEA/IRN), Atherton, and Katz;
                        and approved by Kissinger. Repeated
                        Immediate to Jidda and to Kuwait.
